The paper proposes a novel adaptive oversampling technique for industrial fault diagnostics and prognostics using machine learning algorithms. The paper focuses on addressing the class-imbalance problem in industrial systems, which is a common issue in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
